	"keywords": "Serverless, Serverless Framework, AWS Lambda, Slack, javascript",
	"description": "Serverless architecture is the industry&#x27;s latest buzzword and many of the\nlargest tech companies have begun to embrace it. \n\nIn this article, we&#x27;ll learn what it is and why you should use it. We&#x27;ll also\nset up AWS, create our serverless app, and create a slack app!\n\nWhat is Serverless?\nServerless is a cloud computing paradigm in which the developer no longer has to\nworry about maintaining a server – they just focus on the code. \n\nCloud providers, such as AWS or Azure, are now responsible for exe",
